= Saffron Pokémon Gym\nLeader: Sabrina\pWinning Trainers:\nBlue

#org @sign3
= Saffron Pokémon Gym\nLeader: Sabrina\pWinning Trainers:\nBlue, Mohammed Smith

#org @sign4
= Saffron Pokémon Gym\nLeader: Sabrina\pWinning Trainers:\nBlue, Red

#org @sign5
= Saffron Pokémon Gym\nLeader: Sabrina\pWinning Trainers:\nBlue, Red, Mohammed Smith


